# Global memory index

One-line entries only (≤200 chars). Detail lives in linked files. Workstream-specific memory lives in `<workstream>/_memory/`; cd into a workstream to load it.

## ACTIVE WORK (refresh on each `/save`)

Three buckets. Combined cap ≤12 bullets. If you blow past, collapse or archive.

### Do today / this week
(You can act on these now. Add new in-flight items here.)

### Waiting on others
(Blocked on external input. Monitor, don't push.)

### Parked / deferred
(Off the radar by choice. Dependency missing, between cycles, or paused.)

